{"tid":478244,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"泊車高手們，你地目測呢個位夠唔夠泊一架細車？","createTime":"2017-11-24T01:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T17:12:30.000Z","uid":5632,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"b8dc931e97b48733ac36555ad1009aa11c99e452","tid":478244,"uid":5632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T01:19:51.000Z","msg":"是咁的，話說圖一架七人車個位置本身係一堆雜草，冇泊開車，我個位就係jazz隔離。近日租位比我個人就清晒D雜草，泊多左三架車係我隔離（七人車，mini copper，mini cooper)。<br />\n<br />\n我尋晚用車時出去時得架七人車，部jazz就未返黎，我揸出去時都有D擔心自己返屋企會泊唔到。點撚知我返到黎時就係圖一嘅情況。<br />\n<br />\n我努力試左半個鐘都泊唔到，心灰意冷走去泊住其他地方先。<br />\n<br />\n巴打們你地覺得呢個位夠唔夠泊一架March (同jazz差唔多size) ? 如果夠，應該點泊 ？<br />\n<br />\n圖二同三就係我個位同對面車<br />\n<br />\nPS - 本人未甩p, p左半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">圖一</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/24/090540_c02ed1350ba47a8bbd209ab299d83a45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F24%2F090540_c02ed1350ba47a8bbd209ab299d83a45.jpg&h=b6e9b4ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>圖二</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/24/091731_dbdbe4e9c2efa7171c6fc993b2477c1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F24%2F091731_dbdbe4e9c2efa7171c6fc993b2477c1a.jpg&h=2437da59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>圖三</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/24/091815_335ac1e69b6acf6ffa1d4edd435f9944.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F24%2F091815_335ac1e69b6acf6ffa1d4edd435f9944.jpg&h=5655b35e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0184f21edda66d4cd4c19d5871451463f6f844a2","tid":478244,"uid":32380,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T01:22:18.000Z","msg":"打橫入"},{"pid":"5a220b94f5162909d44a9e2b2e46564f6921be76","tid":478244,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T01:23:10.000Z","msg":"你個部係march?"},{"pid":"0aa1b1865033f949826c1010907417ba7c1e839f","tid":478244,"uid":52215,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T01:23:30.000Z","msg":"我覺得唔夠"},{"pid":"feaef14033c8591d23333ca3e4e6572a0188e26f","tid":478244,"uid":58277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T01:24:49.000Z","msg":"個位泊到都落唔到車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e81e5fde17d112f3f1d49cfb02c20abddbd8025","tid":478244,"uid":52972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T01:25:02.000Z","msg":"入到都開唔到門啦"},{"pid":"0d770d00c31fe18a8d7233a9b66b9633949dc6eb","tid":478244,"uid":2757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T01:27:10.000Z","msg":"泊出邊，一拍兩散"},{"pid":"3837b328747bae694fd231f17d1457b5db83216d","tid":478244,"uid":75320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T01:30:06.000Z","msg":"想知樓主點算"},{"pid":"7b31e150fc990e379126c943e1c13903f8c7f7d6","tid":478244,"uid":150068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T01:30:22.000Z","msg":"日頭先影相啦 咁黑點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a4969bc9bb98f9b0d662903d6b6aeebc0ccad32","tid":478244,"uid":21310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T01:33:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"60e4ef4673ee77cd8e117a08128bec27cde91e04","tid":478244,"uid":5632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T01:37:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個部係march?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nYes."},{"pid":"be95212f764e8cc7d02792ced80ce78c0b82c3da","tid":478244,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T01:38:55.000Z","msg":"唔係高手都知唔夠"},{"pid":"027fa12d6ca190c45d2f526f5b4e2d693cfd81f7","tid":478244,"uid":5632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T01:40:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想知樓主點算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我盡頭有個石屎位，可以泊到一架車。有無車主話果到無人泊，叫我泊住先"},{"pid":"3df3016afe6cd07b284574eab61b2be72100963f","tid":478244,"uid":5632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T01:41:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係高手都知唔夠</blockquote><br />\n咁我今日好租車位比我個人傾下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7227913b6fc5f4d01dfd709e3ef5140322fa420","tid":478244,"uid":15714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T02:11:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係高手都知唔夠</blockquote><br />\n我當佢夠,你下下車尾箱/天窗走咩"},{"pid":"fbd47f1479a074875b657b0d9801eae31de41b85","tid":478244,"uid":46595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T02:19:52.000Z","msg":"叫個地主地下劃返D線啦"},{"pid":"c792b7a87cf5329f2a96449b46c3d2b8299af198","tid":478244,"uid":5632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T02:27:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫個地主地下劃返D線啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根本果到只係夠泊五架車，佢死都要泊六架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918ae22a1fcccb307e14b30d683074ed51e2687b","tid":478244,"uid":46595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T02:41:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>叫個地主地下劃返D線啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根本果到只係夠泊五架車，佢死都要泊六架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁冇計<br />\n真係靠傾"},{"pid":"0dcc39ce8a334e900e10082474e164d3f22133f3","tid":478244,"uid":4209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T02:50:42.000Z","msg":"睇你架車幾大<br />\n不過就算泊到，上落都唔方便啦"},{"pid":"16c0de358db8cb6184f7c8784ce6de35181cbb9c","tid":478244,"uid":35066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T03:27:12.000Z","msg":"夠都出唔到去啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"217c7cdfde601047127306fb23c82f6219f30783","tid":478244,"uid":65335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T03:45:05.000Z","msg":"你拉把尺度下，架車一定闊過個位"},{"pid":"a3d26b21a90832cb8bb94db0c98b4dd7c5008aeb","tid":478244,"uid":19851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T03:50:54.000Z","msg":"入到都唔會泊，夜晚無燈，hi 到或者比人簽名都唔好<br />\n咁辛苦為乜"},{"pid":"e447e7ab767c31535ca096abf32b567c7ffc7bca","tid":478244,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T03:54:49.000Z","msg":"打橫泊係jazz前面"},{"pid":"8f152038252ca0f262bffaed288fb5171a314997","tid":478244,"uid":2161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T03:59:31.000Z","msg":"泊唔到 泊到你點落車"},{"pid":"222ebfc510418c82cab8936de16b10068f671878","tid":478244,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T04:02:57.000Z","msg":"泊唔到"}]}